{
  "stem": "5248.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, they were-- no, Jewish people could not move at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were just-- I mean, once-- a couple of times I tried to-- to leave and make a contact.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I looked very blonde and blue eye.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody-- and my Polish was very good, so nobody expected anything, that I might be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nevertheless, it was very hard to make contact with non-Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, some people-- well, it did not happen to me because I survived, but some people, well, they would just pretend they don't know you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I think they-- they did not want it, or they-- for various reasons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they just-- if you approached them, they-- they just go away, and you could not do it second time because that might be considered molesting them, and there was so much police in every--",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the beginning, it was unsuccessful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Finally-- finally, we found people who-- who were willing to-- to put me up for a couple days until-- and they were not-- I don't know how much they knew, but they were not afraid.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was original agreement, but they never got out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, somebody, again, took me out when I was marching to work, and left me with a family outside of the city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I had to make my way back to the city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By then, the whole camp was gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were-- there were a number of people involved.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And eventually, I stayed with total strangers, and I just start looking for work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "German families were coming a lot to-- to Lwow, and they were looking for maids or things like that, and I-- and since I looked like I said before, I found job with them.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
